306
00:17:49,570 --> 00:17:50,570
Yamamura!

307
00:17:50,570 --> 00:17:53,051
What's the estimated time of death of the victim?

308
00:17:53,051 --> 00:17:54,270
Yes, sir!

309
00:17:55,570 --> 00:17:59,370
