357
00:20:10,631 --> 00:20:12,931
What's this?

358
00:20:12,931 --> 00:20:15,193
That's a water pillow.

359
00:20:15,193 --> 00:20:19,197
You put water inside it and inflate it.

360
00:20:19,197 --> 00:20:21,731
I can't sleep with any other pillow.

361
00:20:21,731 --> 00:20:24,531
I get it! A water pillow!

362
00:20:24,531 --> 00:20:26,931
You filled this up with the smelly water

363
00:20:26,931 --> 00:20:29,207
